244
00:21:55,091 --> 00:22:10,091
<i><font color=#00CED1>Indonesian Translator
~kh4li5h~</font></i></i>

245
00:22:26,640 --> 00:22:28,430
Apa ini?

246
00:22:28,680 --> 00:22:30,310
Kau menginginkannya.

247
00:22:36,850 --> 00:22:39,430
Hati-hati menyetir, Oke?

248
00:22:41,050 --> 00:22:44,050
Mobil ini sangat mahal.

249
00:22:44,050 --> 00:22:45,280
Tidak masalah.

250
00:22:46,600 --> 00:22:49,360
Aku tidak bisa menerimanya.

251
00:22:52,490 --> 00:22:54,960
Joo Young.

252
00:22:56,090 --> 00:22:57,570
Aku...

